    <teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>The Consul General at Peiping (
                        Clubb
                    ) to the Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1949v08</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d68</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">68</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1949-01-18T05:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1949-01-18T05:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-01-18T05:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-01-18T05:00:00-05:00" n="68" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d68">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/1–1849: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Peiping</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clubb</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peiping</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-01-18T18:00:00+08:00">January 18, 1949—6 p. m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 8:29 p. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>61. Re Contel 54, January 18.<note n="6" xml:id="d68fn6">Not printed.</note> I am
                    reliably informed peace delegation comprising 11 persons including ex-mayor Ho
                    Ssu-yuan departed on mission from Peiping 3:30 p. m. today.</p>
                <p>Information received by USIS director about same time was that General Fu Tso-yi
                    had dispatched his own delegate one-half hour previously.</p>
                <p>Sent Department 61, repeated Nanking 57, Shanghai 57.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Clubb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
